    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable per ASME V&V 40 scoping for MRL 2. The CFD hemolysis model predicts RH = 0.83 at the nominal operating point, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Mesh convergence, solver verification, and output comparison evidence collectively support a Medium assurance level conclusion. The credibility assessment team concludes that the model is sufficiently credible to support the COU1 decision for the Class II CPB device.",
